@startuml
title Component Diagram for Web UI (Current-State)

skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Arial"

node "Identity Service" as identity_svc <<System>>
node "Project Service" as project_svc <<System>>
node "Knowledge Service" as knowledge_svc <<System>>
node "Notification Service" as notification_svc <<System>>

package "Web UI (Next.js + React)" {
  [Next.js Pages] as pages
  [Project Dashboard / Report Wizard] as dashboard
  [API Service Layer] as api_layer
  [Context / State Layers] as contexts
  [WebSocket Hook + Service] as ws_client
  [i18n Resources] as i18n
}

pages --> dashboard
pages --> contexts
dashboard --> api_layer
dashboard --> ws_client
pages --> i18n

api_layer -[#blue]> identity_svc : auth endpoints
api_layer -[#blue]> project_svc : campaign/project/datasource flows
api_layer -[#blue]> knowledge_svc : search/chat/report APIs
ws_client -[#purple]> notification_svc : GET /ws

note right of dashboard
Evidence in current source includes:
- project report wizard
- dashboard and trend pages
- websocket hook/service
- i18n and test tooling
end note

@enduml
